Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{3: 'You see darkness once again when you are forcefully disconnected.'}
{3: 'But you can hear someone calling for you eagerly in the trembling darkness.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory39.jpg'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Commandant... Commandant!'}
{3: 'Before you realize, the door of the chamber has been removed by force. You see many familiar faces.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Hey, is it just me? Why's Commandant looking kinda spaced out? Could it be the side effects of the connection chamber?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'I just need some time to recover.', 3: '11', 4: 'I feel a bit dizzy.', 5: '11'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'I just ran a scan on your basic physical conditions, Commandant, but found nothing unusual...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Looks like you should be alright. Take a good rest, Gray Raven Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Let's help Commandant out first.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm sorry, Lucia.", 3: '21', 4: 'Thank you.', 5: '23'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "...It was all because of Cerberus. You don't need to be sorry, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, give me your hand.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "There's nothing to be sorry about. Give me your hand, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "As long as you're safe and sound. And Kamui is back too.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Well, I don't have plans for kicking it in this place. Especially not with some dumbass.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'What did you say?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "P-please calm down. I don't think Karenina meant it...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'And so the fight starts...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: "I see... This is how Gray Raven is like. I've got to paint it down.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's always getting busier and busier when you are around, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Well, I kind of like it.', 3: '44', 4: 'People often come with troubles.', 5: '47'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'But you always handle everything well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'This is nice.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's great when everyone comes together, Commandant. I hope we can spend every year, every month, and every holiday like this.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm sure we will.", 3: '53'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory17.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: "Happy April Fool's Day, Asimov.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "Stop digressing. You took the connection chamber out, didn't you? And you let those outside the project know about it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Does it really matter? I've got the discovery of the century on my hands though. The Gray Raven Commandant can use the remote connection technique almost perfectly.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "But you knew that long ago, didn't you?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "Stop answering my questions with questions... Whatever, I'd suggest you leave the commandant of Gray Raven alone.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "So we aren't authorized to know about it. Is that what you're saying?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'Tsk. A boring squad with a commandant like that one.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "Don't go yet. I've got something else to tell you.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'What is it? Have you finally found a commandant for us?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "That's right.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'If the report results are right, you\'ll soon be able to formally meet a commandant, who can use the remote connection technique "perfectly."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Hmph... Haha, great news. Wait, is this an April Fool's joke?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "Do I look like someone with such a terrible sense of humor? Get Noctis and 21 back to Babylonia ASAP. You're about to have your final adjustments.", 4: '1'}
